🌎 It’s #EarthMonth and @GoodwillSoCal invited me to upcycle an outfit! ✂️ Check out my designs at #THRIFTCYCLE on view at Goodwill SoCal’s flagship store in Atwater Village. 

♻️ #Goodwill’s priority is to ensure that each donation is given a chance at a new life, through re-use, repurposing, or recycling. When you donate or shop at your local Goodwill, you not only help people in our community, you also help protect the planet!
 
🔗 www.goodwillsocal.org/thriftcycle
📍 Goodwill SoCal Atwater Village Store, 3150 N. San Fernando Rd. Los Angeles, CA
